Package edu.umd.cs.psl.model.kernel.predicateconstraint

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DomainRangeConstraintKernel
    Produces GroundDomainRangeConstraints.
    GroundDomainRangeConstraint
    GroundPredicateConstraint uses a PredicateConstraintKernel as a template and operates on an Entity involved in the associated Predicate, providing the ability to ground Atoms involving the Predicate.
    GroundSymmetryConstraint
    Constrains two GroundAtoms to be equal.
    SymmetryConstraintKernel
    Induces GroundSymmetryConstraints between Atoms of a binary StandardPredicate with symmetric arguments.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DomainRangeConstraintType
    PredicateConstraintType provides a method of specifying predicate constraints as used by the DomainRangeConstraintKernel.
